---
// Hero Contacto - Sección hero para página Contacto
---

<section class="relative min-h-[65vh] lg:min-h-[60vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-black pt-32 md:pt-36 lg:pt-44">
  <!-- Background Image -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img src="/imagenes/imagen4.webp" alt="Contacto S3A Industrial" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/70 via-black/50 to-black/70"></div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Background pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 40%, rgba(170, 126, 86, 0.05) 40%, rgba(170, 126, 86, 0.05) 60%, transparent 60%);"></div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-16 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-white">
      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav style="font-family: var(--font-body);" class="text-xs md:text-sm mb-5 opacity-80 tracking-widest uppercase flex items-center gap-2">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium text-white/70">Inicio</a>
        <span class="text-white/40">•</span>
        <span class="text-white font-semibold">Contacto</span>
      </nav>
      
      <!-- Title -->
      <h1 style="
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #b0c8d8 50%, #334c60 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.8));
      " class="text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl xl:text-9xl font-normal mb-6 leading-none uppercase">
        Contáctenos
      </h1>

      <!-- Accent line -->
      <div class="w-20 h-[3px] mb-6" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffffff, #334c60);"></div>
      
      <!-- Subtitle -->
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); text-shadow: 0 1px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);" class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl max-w-xl mb-8 leading-relaxed font-light text-white/90">
        Solicite nuestros servicios técnicos especializados. Nuestro equipo 
        está listo para atender sus necesidades de mantenimiento industrial.
      </p>
      
      <!-- Contact methods -->
      <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading);" class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 md:gap-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/10 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl backdrop-blur">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white/80" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Llámanos</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/10 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl backdrop-blur">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white/80" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Escríbenos</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/10 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl backdrop-blur">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white/80" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Agenda una cita</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Floating contact elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-24 right-16 w-6 h-6 border-2 border-golden/40 rounded transform rotate-45 animate-bounce"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-20 w-4 h-4 bg-golden-light/60 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-12 w-8 h-1 bg-rust/50 rounded animate-pulse delay-700"></div>

  <!-- Golden bottom separator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-[3px]" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, #aa7e56 30%, #cca373 60%, #aa7e56 80%, transparent 100%);"></div>
</section>